<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.3">
<l>arukali lāya peruñcī ramararka ḷāti mutalvaṉ</l>
<l>karukiya nīlanaṉ mēṉi vaṇṇaṉcen tāmaraik kaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>poruciṟaip puḷḷuvan tēṟum pūmaka ḷārtaṉik kēḷva</l>
<l>ṉorukati yiṉcuvai tantiṭ ṭoḻivila ṉeṉṉō ṭuṭaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The first beginning of the immortals of great excellence who are close,</l>
<l>the one with darkened blue colour on [his] good body, Kṛṣṇa with red lotus eyes,</l>
<l>the only husband of the flower lady who joyfully mounts a bird with beating wings,</l>
<l>the one who, giving the taste of a refuge, is without end is with me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
